WHAT IS SECURITY IN OUR PROJECT?
---------------------------------
  - Passwords are hashed with SHA-256 (nobody can read them)
  - Every request needs a token
  - Tokens are random (64 characters)
  - When you log in again, the old token stops working
  - Admin and user have different permissions
  - CI/CD tests code automatically before it goes live


